Package lemming.pos

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPosDao
    Defines a part of speech DAO by extending interface IDao.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Pos
    Class representing a part of speech.
    PosActionPanelColumn
    A custom column with actions for parts of speech and and a filter panel as filter.
    PosAutoCompleteTextField
    A text field able to auto-complete part of speech names.
    PosDao
    Represents a Data Access Object providing data operations for parts of speech.
    PosDeleteConfirmPanel
    A panel containing a modal window dialog asking if a part of speech shall be deleted.
    PosDeleteDeniedPanel
    A panel containing a modal window dialog stating that a part of speech could not be deleted.
    PosEditPage
    A page containing a part of speech edit form.
    PosIndexPage
    An index page that lists all available parts of speech in a data table.
    PosResource
    A resource for part of speech data.
    PosTextField
    A text field converting pos names to parts of speech.
